OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK probes using Russian    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fassets for Ukraine defence 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has asked the Bank of   
OL,6, England to look at options for using   
OL,7, Russian sovereign assets to fund       
OL,8, Ukraine's war effort, Chancellor Jeremy
OL,9, Hunt has told the BBC.                 
OL,11,FMr Hunt said finance ministers around  
OL,12,Fthe world had discussed what more they 
OL,13,Fcould do, beyond sanctions, to disrupt 
OL,14,FRussia's ability to pay for the war.   
OL,16,F"This is an illegal war," Mr Hunt said.
OL,18,F"We need to do everything we can to    
OL,19,Fmake sure that Russia cannot continue  
OL,20,Fto fund it."                           
